      "cookedHtml": "<p>Hi everybody<br />\nI wanna use a board total in another board and I’ve made a scenario by Make but the output is incorrect . I attached a video of my scenario. please help me to solve the issue.<br />\nThanks<br />\n</p><div class=\"video-container\">\n    \n      \n      <a href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/2X/6/63bd82dee042649c723e9701a43b17ab502d0db1.mov\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/2X/6/63bd82dee042649c723e9701a43b17ab502d0db1.mov</a>\n    \n  </div><p></p>"
