      "id": 90398,
      "postNumber": 2,
      "createdAt": "2022-07-05T09:10:22.584Z",
      "author": "JCorrell (Jim - The Monday Man)",
      "cookedHtml": "<p><a class=\"mention\" href=\"/u/hamiiiid\">@hamiiiid</a></p>\n<p>I see two issues:<br />\n</p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/2X/d/d98cf4df6f9e3e65dbf61b11251e5529491ca2bf.jpeg\" title=\"image\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/optimized/2X/d/d98cf4df6f9e3e65dbf61b11251e5529491ca2bf_2_289x375.jpeg\" alt=\"image\" width=\"289\" height=\"375\" /><div class=\"meta\">\n<span class=\"filename\">image</span><span class=\"informations\">494×639 43.5 KB</span>\n</div></a></div><p></p>\n<p>Your map() function in the formulas for both Variable values should read: <code>map(3.array;numbers163)</code></p>\n<hr />\n<p></p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/2X/3/31b1c2d31880609f9867877bf12db09f04209ecf.png\" title=\"image\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/optimized/2X/3/31b1c2d31880609f9867877bf12db09f04209ecf_2_288x375.png\" alt=\"image\" width=\"288\" height=\"375\" /><div class=\"meta\">\n<span class=\"filename\">image</span><span class=\"informations\">477×618 104 KB</span>\n</div></a></div><p></p>\n<p>Your Value formula here should read: <code>round(sum(map(3.array;numbers163)))</code></p>\n<hr />\n<p>Jim - <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/TheMondayMan?sub_confirmation=1\">The Monday Man (YouTube Channel)</a><br />\n<strong><a href=\"https://themondayman.com/make/\">What is Make &amp; How can it help you?</a></strong><br />\n<strong><a href=\"https://themondayman.com/custom/\">We Create Custom Solutions</a></strong><br />\n<strong><a href=\"https://themondayman.com/tutorial/\">Schedule a 1-on-1 Tutorial Session (for monday, Make &amp; gardening)</a></strong></p>"
    },
